How it Works: Contact us with what you want your website to be/what you want it to do, along with any ideas for what it should look like. We then provide a cost, and the website's building will start when your transaction is complete (Cash Only). We will also provide a time estimate and updates on the progress of your sites construction. Once the site is finished, we transfer it to your domain (you must have a domain or a github domain will be used), and you finalize any things you would like to change. If you are not satisfied, you will get a 100% cash refund and we will take down the site.